# DnD Companion — Backend Domain Modülleri

Her kaynak tipi kendi NestJS modülünde ([CODE-003]). Alt feature'lar modül içi alt klasör — ayrı top-level modül değil.

## Modül Haritası

| Modül | Sorumluluk | Alt klasörler |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `campaigns/` | Campaign CRUD, invite, members, dm-notes | `members/`, `invite/`, `dm-notes/` |
| `characters/` | Sheet CRUD, campaign assign, visibility, live fields REST | `dto/` |
| `homebrew/` | 6 tip homebrew, draft/publish | `dto/` |
| `collections/` | Kullanıcı koleksiyonu (published homebrew ref) | — |
| `users/` | Profil read/update, self deactivate | `dto/` |
| `reference/` | Resmi 5e read-only seed verisi | — |
| `uploads/` | Presigned URL | `dto/` |
| `email/` | Transactional email (auth akışları) | — |

`auth/`, `admin/`, `websocket/`, `common/` → ilgili 11/12/16/17 kuralları.

## Modül İç Yapı

```
<module>/
  <module>.module.ts
  <module>.controller.ts      # veya alt feature controller'ları
  <module>.service.ts
  dto/
  <feature>/                   # opsiyonel
    <feature>.controller.ts
    <feature>.service.ts
```

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — campaigns alt feature ayrı controller, aynı modül
@Module({
  controllers: [CampaignsController, MembersController, InviteController, DmNotesController],
  providers: [CampaignsService, MembersService, InviteService, DmNotesService],
})
export class CampaignsModule {}

// ✗ Yanlış — invite logic'i campaigns.service.ts içinde 500 satır
```

Controller → Service tek yönlü; service'ler arası çapraz çağrı dikkatli (circular dependency → forwardRef veya shared helper).

## Service Sorumluluğu Şablonu

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — find → policy → mutate
async update(id: string, user: AuthUser, dto: UpdateCampaignDto) {
  const campaign = await this.prisma.campaign.findUnique({ where: { id } });
  if (!campaign) throw new NotFoundException();
  if (!CampaignPolicy.canUpdate(user, campaign)) {
    throw new ForbiddenException({ error: 'FORBIDDEN', message: 'You do not have permission to update this campaign' });
  }
  return this.prisma.campaign.update({ where: { id }, data: dto });
}

// ✗ Yanlış — policy yok veya ADMIN bypass service'de unutulmuş
async update(id: string, dto: UpdateCampaignDto) {
  return this.prisma.campaign.update({ where: { id }, data: dto });
}
```

Create: `ownerId` / `userId` her zaman `user.id` — client'tan kabul etme.

## Campaign Domain

- Private kaynak [AUTH-004]; liste yalnızca owner + member campaign'leri.
- DM = `owner_id`; invite token regenerate/disable DM only.
- `POST /invite/:token/join` — auth zorunlu; `campaign_members` insert.
- DM notes: yalnızca campaign DM (service policy).
- Member delete: DM only; DM kendini member'dan silemez (owner zaten DM).

## Character Domain

- Builder/sheet aynı entity [W-002] — status field yok.
- `campaign_id` nullable, max bir campaign [AUTH-006].
- Assign: user hedef campaign üyesi olmalı; önceki atama clear veya atomic swap.
- `visibility`: `PUBLIC` | `PRIVATE`; toggle owner only.
- Live fields REST: `PATCH /characters/:id/live` — DM veya owner; WS broadcast gateway üzerinden (16).

## Homebrew Domain

- `source`: `OFFICIAL` (seed, read-only user write) | `HOMEBREW`.
- State: `DRAFT` → `PUBLISHED` / unpublish [W-003].
- `data` JSONB: tip bazlı Zod (`packages/shared/schemas/homebrew/`).
- Galeri `GET /homebrew`: yalnızca `PUBLISHED`; misafir okuyabilir.
- Publish: `@RequireVerifiedEmail()` + owner policy.

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — JSONB Zod validate
const parsed = spellDataSchema.safeParse(dto.data);
if (!parsed.success) {
  throw new BadRequestException({
    error: 'VALIDATION_FAILED',
    message: 'Invalid data for this homebrew type',
    details: parsed.error.issues.map((i) => ({
      field: `data.${i.path.join('.')}`,
      issue: i.message,
    })),
  });
}

// ✗ Yanlış — data'yı doğrulamadan JSONB'ye yazma
data: dto.data as Prisma.InputJsonValue,
```

## Collections Domain

- `collection_items` join: user ↔ homebrew_item.
- Add/remove: verified user; homebrew `PUBLISHED` olmalı (unpublish sonrası ref kalır — UI rozeti FE).
- Idempotent add → `409` veya silent success — spec'e uy (`docs/03` Bölüm 9).

## Users Domain

- `GET /users/me` — tam profil (email dahil).
- `GET /users/:id` — başkası için `username` + `avatarUrl` only [PII].
- `PATCH /users/me` — profil; email değişimi MVP dışı (varsa doc kontrol).
- Self deactivate: `is_active=false`, refresh revoke.

## Reference Domain

- Tamamen read-only; tüm route `@Public()`.
- Seed'ten gelen official homebrew/reference — user PATCH yok.
- Cursor pagination + ILIKE search (`docs/03` Bölüm 11).

## Uploads Domain

- `POST /uploads/presign` — verified user.
- MIME: png/jpeg/webp only; max 5 MB [D-005].
- Magic-byte doğrulama service'de; SVG reddedilir.
- Presigned URL; dosya doğrudan object storage'a — API body'den binary yok.

## Email Domain

- `EmailService` inject; auth service çağırır.
- Template metinleri İngilizce.
- SMTP cred env'den; log'da credential yok.

## DTO Konvansiyonu

Dosya adı: `create-*.dto.ts`, `update-*.dto.ts`, `assign-campaign.dto.ts`. `class-validator` decorator'ları; optional alanlar `@IsOptional()`.

Liste endpoint'leri: `ListQueryDto` import (`common/dto/`).

## Modüller Arası Bağımlılık

| İzinli | Kaçın |
| --- | --- |
| `characters` → `campaigns` membership check (service) | `campaigns` → `characters` tight coupling |
| Herhangi → `email/EmailService` | Domain → `admin/` |
| `characters` → `websocket` gateway broadcast (live update) | Circular module imports |

Websocket gateway export: `WebsocketModule` exports gateway; `CharactersService` inject edip `broadcastLiveUpdate` çağırır.

## Response Serializer

Entity → API camelCase Prisma default. Hassas alan strip: `password_hash` asla; `email` yalnızca owner/admin context.

Liste response: `{ data, nextCursor, hasMore }`.

## Invite Token Yönetimi [W-001]

- `invite_token` nullable — disable = `NULL`
- Regenerate: yeni crypto random token; eski link geçersiz
- `GET /invite/:token` — public preview (auth yok); join auth zorunlu
- `InvalidInviteTokenException` → 404

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — join
if (!campaign.inviteToken || campaign.inviteToken !== hashVerify(token)) {
  throw new InvalidInviteTokenException();
}
if (await this.isMember(campaign.id, user.id)) {
  throw new AlreadyMemberException();
}
```

## DM Notes

Yalnızca campaign DM CRUD. Player read yok (campaign private zaten — üye read campaign context'inde). Reorder endpoint: `PATCH .../reorder` — sıra array validate.

## Live Fields REST → WS Köprüsü

`CharactersService.updateLiveFields`:
1. Policy: owner veya campaign DM
2. Prisma update allowed fields only (`hitPointsCurrent`, `temporaryHitPoints`, `conditions`, `deathSaves`)
3. `websocketGateway.broadcastLiveUpdate(campaignId, payload)`

REST persist; WS notify — WS tek başına kaynak değil.

## Homebrew Tipleri

6 alt tip: SPELL, MONSTER, FEAT, BACKGROUND, MAGIC_ITEM, SUBCLASS — `type` enum + ilgili Zod schema. `source`: OFFICIAL (seed) | HOMEBREW.

Publish: `status = PUBLISHED`, `publishedAt = now()`. Unpublish: galeriden düşer; collection ref kalır.

## Collection İş Kuralları

- Add: homebrew `PUBLISHED` olmalı
- Duplicate add → `409` `ALREADY_IN_COLLECTION`
- Remove: idempotent veya 404 — spec'e uy

## Reference Read-Only

Seed JSON → `prisma/seed-data/`. API salt read; filtre `search`, `source`, cursor. Classes/races shared constants ile uyumlu (`packages/shared`).

## Upload Presign Akışı

1. Client `POST /uploads/presign` { contentType, fileSize }
2. Service validate MIME + size
3. Presigned PUT URL + `publicUrl` döner
4. Client storage'a PUT
5. Client ilgili entity'yi `bannerUrl` / `avatarUrl` PATCH

Sunucu binary upload yok (MVP).

## Email Service Kullanımı

`EmailService.sendVerificationEmail`, `sendPasswordResetEmail` — template İngilizce. AuthService çağırır; domain modülleri email modülüne doğrudan bağlanmaz (auth hariç).

## Domain Event / Side Effect Özeti

| Olay | Yan etki |
| --- | --- |
| Campaign member join | WS `campaign:member-joined` |
| Member remove | WS `campaign:member-left` |
| User deactivate | refresh revoke |
| Admin deactivate | + audit (17) |
| Character live update | WS `character:live-update` |

## Anti-pattern'ler

- ❌ Repository katmanı ekleme
- ❌ `ownerId`'yi request body'den alma
- ❌ Official/seed içeriğe user write endpoint
- ❌ Homebrew `data` için class-validator ile derin JSON validate
- ❌ Campaign'i public listeleme
- ❌ Character'ı campaign üyeliği olmadan cross-campaign assign
- ❌ Collection'a DRAFT homebrew ekleme (business rule ihlali)
- ❌ Reference modülüne write endpoint
- ❌ Upload'da SVG veya sunucu taraflı buffer upload (MVP presign only)
- ❌ Live field update'te WS broadcast unutma
- ❌ Invite token plain DB'de saklama
- ❌ DM notes'a player write endpoint

## Circular Dependency Önleme

`CampaignsService` ↔ `CharactersService` — membership check için prisma direct veya shared helper; modül circular import'tan kaçın.

## Official Homebrew Immutability (User Path)

`source === OFFICIAL` → user `homebrew.service` write metodları erken `403`. Admin path ayrı.

